  "texts": [
    "In addition, detailed and structured concerns and limitations were uncovered.",
    "Moreover, measures to use GAI tools effectively and ethically were analyzed and organized.",
    "These findings will allow for a broader understanding and provide further directions for future research.",
    "In addition, the findings will help various stakeholders in different sectors including researchers, reviewers, policymakers, and developers take into consideration their roles and responsibilities to overcome possible drawbacks and enhance academic research productivity and quality.",
    "This study presented systematic literature on applications of GAI tools in various tasks of academic research workflow and peer review process."
  ]
